text: Dan Mircea Ionel is an electrical engineer working for Vestas Wind Turbines R&D; in Fox Point, Wisconsin. He was named a Fellow of the Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE) in 2013 for his contributions to the analysis, design and, manufacturing of high efficiency electric machines. == References == Category:Fellow Members of the IEEE Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Dan Mircea Ionel
